ow performing countries but positively in developed and high performing countries these results are unaffected by a wide variety of robustness and specification tests providing confidence in the need for nuanced application of reform ideas also available as asian development bank economic working paper no 296 download adb economic working paper no 296 topics international resources efficiency hoover institution 434 galvez mall room 151 stanford university stanford ca 94305 6010 phone 650.736 0942 fax 650.723 1687 2012 hanushek net questions or comments member log in stanford university
